close_reason: "All 11 audit phases completed successfully. Build passes (1087/1087 tests), security clean, search working (score 0.98), calendar 4 views verified, SDK 78 exports, telemetry E2E ingest confirmed (HTTP 200), Sentry 0 code bugs."
body: "AUDIT RESULTS (2026-05-02 v2026.5.1-2):\n\nSECURITY (PASS): check-secrets.mjs passes clean. No credentials/IPs/tokens in tracked files. Sentry beforeSend scrubs sntr[ysu]_ patterns. Telemetry sanitizeString redacts emails/tokens/paths.\n\nBUILD (PASS): pnpm build clean. TypeScript strict. 1087/1087 tests pass across 81 files.\n\nSEARCH (PASS): Hybrid mode (keyword+semantic) working. qwen3-embedding:0.6b + LanceDB. 644 items vectorized. Score 0.98 for relevant queries. Auto-indexing on mutations confirmed.\n\nCALENDAR (PASS): 4 views (agenda/day/week/month) x 3 formats (toon/json/markdown). Recurrence expansion (daily/weekly/monthly/yearly). by_weekday/by_month_day/exdates/until/count/interval all working.\n\nSDK (PASS): 78 exports including defineExtension. 56 commands in contracts. 2 extensions active (beads, todos). package.json exports resolve correctly.\n\nTELEMETRY (PASS): pm-cli.unbrained.dev accepts events (HTTP 200). pm.unbrained.dev (Grafana) accessible. Queue flush with retry/backoff working. OTel span export configured.\n\nSENTRY (PASS): 8 issues total, all PmCliError (user-facing). Zero unexpected exceptions. Free plan tracesSampleRate 0.2 appropriate. Source map pipeline working.\n\nCODE QUALITY (PASS): Zero any types. Zero process.exit(). Utilities canonical (toNonEmptyString, toErrorMessage, nowIso single definitions). 50,275 source lines across 99 files.\n\nPERFORMANCE (ACCEPTABLE): list 0.95s, search 1.58s, context 1.17s, calendar 0.74s for 644 items. Only sync I/O at startup (Sentry version + package.json).\n\nOPEN IMPROVEMENTS: (1) pm-6c3h main.ts 5796 lines decomposition, (2) pm-p0p1 HTTP fetch pattern consolidation, (3) pm-f6wr list performance for 1000+ item projects."
